<section id="Editing_a_Repository" remap="TID_15376">
	<title>Editing a Repository</title>
	<para>
		Use the following procedure to edit information about the repository, such as the name and path.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Edit Repository Information</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to menu:Infrastructure[Repositories].
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the repository to edit.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Configuration)</guibutton>, and then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1851.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guibutton>(Edit the Selected Repository)</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In <guilabel>Basic Info</guilabel>, edit the name and path to connect to the repository.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>Save</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>